name: Bugswarm-renesas
body:
## bugswarm-renesas: 

A bugswarm connector for Renesas 8- and 16-bit microcontrollers.

### Supported Boards

*  RL78/G13 Demonstration Kit (YRDKRL78G13) with the Redpine companion WiFi Card (RS-RL78G13-2200CC)

### Status

*  The following sensors are exposed:
    1. 3-axis Accelerometer
    1. Temperature
    1. Ambient Light
    1. Potentiometer Position
    1. Sound Level
    1. Button status.
tagline: A BUGswarm connector for Renesas 8- and 16-bit microcontrollers.
